snippet.title: Rocket League® - New RLCS Intro Debut
snippet.description:
Check out the new high-octane intro to the Rocket League Championship Series (RLCS). You can expect this intro to start the Season 8 World Championship in Madrid, Spain, and to introduce RLCS Season 9 streams and beyond! 

Want to attend the World Championship in person? Grab your tickets here: http://tickets.rlesports.gg 
If you’re planning on watching online, tune in on December 13-15 at 6 a.m. PST (2 p.m. UTC) here: https://www.twitch.tv/rocketleague
